OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFriday will generally be a
OL,6,Fbrighter day than of late, though with
OL,7,Fa cold and sometimes blustery wind
OL,8,Fblowing. There will also be some
OL,9,Fshowers, these most widespread in the
OL,10,Fnorth and west, where locally heavy
OL,11,Fand in places wintry.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThere will be a mixture of
OL,14,Fclear spells and scattered showers
OL,15,Fthis evening. The showers will become
OL,16,Fmore confined to the northwest
OL,17,Fovernight. A widespread frost forming,
OL,18,Fwith icy patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
