OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAfter a cold start, there
OL,6,Fwill be sunny spells and further
OL,7,Fshowers on Saturday. Most of the
OL,8,Fshowers are likely in the northwest.
OL,9,FLighter winds overall, and feeling
OL,10,Fless chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
